title: NutriBullet: Apple Spice Pie Smoothie Recipe
description:
This delicious dessert Blast will satisfy your sweet tooth without the guilt! Antioxidant-rich berries and filling oats, blood sugar-regulating cinnamon and walnuts packed with omega-3 fatty acids all combine to give you healthy, tasty results.

RECIPE:

1 Cup Spinach
1   Apple
½ Cup Blueberries
⅓ Cup Oats
½ Teaspoon Cinnamon
5   Walnuts
1 Teaspoon Chia Seeds
1 Pinch Nutmeg
1 Cup Almond Milk
Ice Cubes *

*Ice cubes should not exceed 25% of your total ingredients.
